What you need to know:

Klopp has earned near God-like status on Merseyside for delivering a sixth European Cup and a first league title for 30 years to LiverpoolHopes the Champions League could prove the salvation of a disappointing season were also dashed as Real ran riot in the first 45 minutes in Madrid last week to open up a commanding first-leg leadLiverpool can claim to have suffered more than most from an entire season behind closed doors